WEBVTT

00:00:00.756 --> 00:00:05.156
Listen, I'm British-born
and by a Nigerian raised.

00:00:05.196 --> 00:00:07.876
There were expectations,

00:00:07.916 --> 00:00:09.836
different ways I was supposed to go.

00:00:09.836 --> 00:00:11.556
My career options for one,

00:00:11.556 --> 00:00:13.956
some of you may already know.

00:00:13.996 --> 00:00:17.156
As an African, you get three choices.

00:00:17.196 --> 00:00:19.356
Please, repeat after me.

00:00:19.716 --> 00:00:22.836
You are going to be a doctor --

00:00:22.876 --> 00:00:24.076
Audience: A doctor.

00:00:24.076 --> 00:00:25.236
FB: A lawyer.

00:00:25.276 --> 00:00:26.436
Audience: A lawyer.

00:00:26.476 --> 00:00:28.516
FB: Or a business man.

00:00:28.516 --> 00:00:30.436
Audience: Or a businessman.